  "description": "The Vivax brand refrigerator is a fairly easy-to-use model that is suitable for an ordinary family consisting of several people. The total usable volume is 224 liters, with 146 liters in the refrigerator compartment and 78 liters in the freezer compartment. Inside there is everything necessary for the proper organization of the workspace. The refrigerator compartment is equipped with four shelves made of durable tempered glass, a pull-out container for storing vegetables and fruits and several side shelves for bottles and eggs. The freezer compartment has three pull-out containers made of transparent plastic so you can control the contents. Vivax CF-310 NFX uses Total No Frost technology, which makes the device easier to maintain and eliminates the need to manually defrost the refrigerator and freezer compartments. And the No Frost Multi Air Flow cooling technology provides dry air inside the refrigerator, which promotes long-term storage of fresh food. Also among the advantages are quiet operation, interior LED lighting, a touch control panel and the ability to reverse the doors.",
